high_descs: Begin walking across the room, then hang a right and walk forward, turn right and walk up to the end of the counter.
Pick up the apple off of the counter.
Turn around and walk towards the wall, then hang a left and walk over to the microwave on the small white table.
Open the microwave and put the apple inside then close the door, turn on the microwave, after a couple seconds open the microwave and take the apple out, then close the microwave.
Walk over to the black shelving unit in between the trash bag and counter behind you.
Put the heated apple on the front right corner of the black shelving unit.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated apple on top of a black shelving unit.

high_descs: Take a step forward then turn right and walk to the counter that's to the left of the sink then turn right to face it when you get to it.
Pick up the apple that's in front of you to the left of the black cup.
Turn around and turn left when you are almost to the white table then walk to the garbage then turn right and walk to the wall then turn left and walk to the microwave.
Cook the apple in the microwave then take it back out and close the door.
Walk back to where you got the apple then take a step to your left.
Put the apple on the small black table to the right of the lettuce.
anns.task_desc: Put a microwaved apple on the table.

high_descs: Walk straight to the end of the kitchen and turn right to face the white counter top.
Pick the apple up from off of the counter.
Turn around, go to the left and then to the right to face the microwave.
Microwave the apple in the the microwave.
Turn around then go straight to the end of the kitchen then to the right to face the black table.
Place the apple on the black table.
anns.task_desc: Place the microwaved apple on the black table in the corner of the kitchen.
